quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,84,"Maaku: "Men gom…óinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e Taaniraa…ďe …ďen e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e Annabaa…ďe …ďen immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e ma…ď…ďe, Menen wonan de Mo ko men jebbilii…ďe"."
  3,85,"Kala …óa…ď…ďu…óo ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o ja…ďaŇčtaake …óum, on …óon ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e pertu…ďe …ďen."
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yim…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe …ďe seedii won de Nulaa…óo on ko goonga, …ďanngannduyeeji …óin arii …ďe? Alla Fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  3,87,"∆Āen …óon, jo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, ko no fawii …ďe kuddi Alla ndin e Maleykaaji en e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe denndaangal."
  3,88,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake lepte …óen, …ďe wonaali nee6nantee…ďe."
  3,89,"Si wonaa …ďeen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óuum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo."
  3,90,"Pellet, …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe, refti …ďe …ďeydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol ma…ď…ďe ja…ďetaake; ko …ďeen …óon noni majju…ďe …ďeen."
  3,91,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heerer…ďe, gooto e ma…ď…ďe ja…ďaŇčtaake, leydi ndin tew kaŇčŇče; hay si o sootorii …óum. ∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe, …ďe alaa walloo…ďe."